01:10:33.573 --> 01:10:36.011
anche, vede, lei prende blocchi da loro.

01:10:38.227 --> 01:10:38.952
Fuma?

01:10:39.452 --> 01:10:40.154
No.

01:10:40.896 --> 01:10:44.217
